00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:06.200
Oke.

00:01:06.720 --> 00:01:07.720
Aku pergi, Neelam.

00:01:08.320 --> 00:01:09.320
Mama.

00:01:09.520 --> 00:01:10.840
Pergi, sayang.

